Author: strugglingpianist
Text: this is so brave. i saw a girl post something like this on her main a few months ago with like 1k+ followers. all super positive comments. I hope yours is just as well received 😊

Author: jazminonacloud
Text: Hey, I just want to let you know that I read it all. I am sending all of my love over the internet waves because I know exactly how you’re feeling. You’re panicked and feel like you’re spiraling. Just know that this community is here to ground you when you need it ❤️ thank you so much for sharing your story.
